title: october 27: a mini crash and a major star (with Julien Baker)
description:
In this episode of 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia analyzes a mini stock market crash and does a little primer on stocks in general. Maia also looks back on a lost musical icon. Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
